Class DFID_search

  • java.lang.Object
    • DFID_search
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    search_algorithm

    public class DFID_search
extends java.lang.Object
implements search_algorithm
    This class represents a recursive DFID algorithm with loop-avoidance. Note that the algorithm does not necessarily find the cheapest path but rather finds the shortest path. This class implements the search_algorithm interface.
    Author:
    Ori Ben-Hamo
